ENDING_12, ENDING_13, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGD R (nolock) left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:1 and FISCAL_YEAR=:2 and select LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, sum(ENDING_01),sum(ENDING_02),sum(ENDING_03),sum(ENDING_04),sum(ENDING_05),sum(ENDING_06),sum(ENDING_07),sum(ENDING_08), ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_08, ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_09, ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_10, ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_11, ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_12, ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_13 FROM ( select P.LINE_NO,X.ACCOUNT_NO,X.[DESCRIPTION],X.COLUMN_NO,X.FONT_STYLE,X.NOTES, BEGINNING_AMT,ENDING_01, ENDING_02, ENDING_03, ENDING_04, ENDING_05, ENDING_06, ENDING_07, ENDING_08, ENDING_09, ENDING_10, ENDING_11, ENDING_12, ENDING_13, OPERATION, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGP P (nolock) LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD D (nolock) ON D.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND D.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND D.LINE_NO=P.FROM_LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD X (nolock) ON X.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND X.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND X.LINE_NO=P.LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_BALANCE B (nolock) ON B.CO_ID=D.CO_ID AND B.BR_ID=:1 AND FISCAL_YEAR=:2 AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=D.ACCOUNT_NO AND CURR_ID=':3' :7 WHERE P.CO_ID=':4' AND P.REPORT_NO=:5 ) T2 ) Y group by LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER ORDER BY LINE_NO

select TA.LINE_NO,TA.ACCOUNT_NO,TA.[DESCRIPTION],TA.COLUMN_NO,TA.FONT_STYLE,TA.NOTES, TA.SALDO_01,TA.SALDO_02,TA.SALDO_03,TA.SALDO_04,TA.SALDO_05,TA.SALDO_06,TA.SALDO_07, TA.SALDO_08,TA.SALDO_09,TA.SALDO_10,TA.SALDO_11,TA.SALDO_12,TA.SALDO_13, TA.COST_CENTER, S.GCM_ID, S.GCM_NUM, S.DESCRIPTION as BeginTag, S.GCM_NOTE2 as EndTag, S.GCM_NOTE3 as NumericTag, S.GCM_NOTE4 as ColorMagic, C.OcrName from ( select LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0))/:6 SALDO_01, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0))/:6 SALDO_02, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_03-ENDING_02,0))/:6 SALDO_03, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_04-ENDING_03,0))/:6 SALDO_04, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_05-ENDING_04,0))/:6 SALDO_05, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_06-ENDING_05,0))/:6 SALDO_06, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_07-ENDING_06,0))/:6 SALDO_07, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0))/:6 SALDO_08, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0))/:6 SALDO_09, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0))/:6 SALDO_10, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0))/:6 SALDO_11, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0))/:6 SALDO_12, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0))/:6 SALDO_13, COST_CENTER AS COST_CENTER from ( select LINE_NO,R.ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, BEGINNING_AMT,ENDING_01, ENDING_02, ENDING_03, ENDING_04, ENDING_05, ENDING_06, ENDING_07, ENDING_08, ENDING_09, ENDING_10, ENDING_11, ENDING_12, ENDING_13, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGD R (nolock) left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:1 and FISCAL_YEAR=:2 and CURR_ID=':3' AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=R.ACCOUNT_NO :7 WHERE R.CO_ID=':4' AND REPORT_NO=:5 AND LINE_TYPE<>'P' ) T1 group by LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER
union all
select LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, sum(ENDING_01),sum(ENDING_02),sum(ENDING_03),sum(ENDING_04),sum(ENDING_05),sum(ENDING_06),sum(ENDING_07),sum(ENDING_08), COST_CENTER, ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_01, ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_02, ENDING_04, ENDING_05, ENDING_06, ENDING_07, ENDING_08, ENDING_09, ENDING_10, ENDING_11, ENDING_12, ENDING_13, OPERATION, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGP P (nolock) LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD D (nolock) ON D.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND D.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND D.LINE_NO=P.FROM_LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD X (nolock) ON X.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND X.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND Y group by LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER ) TA left join ( select * from sys_gcm (nolock) where condition = 'FONT' ) S on TA.FONT_STYLE = S.GCM_ID left join OOCR C (nolock) on C.OcrCode = TA.COST_CENTER ORDER BY LINE_NO

select S.GCM_NOTE1 as TypeName, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0))/:1 SALDO_01, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0))/:1 SALDO_02, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_03-ENDING_02,0))/:1 SALDO_03, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_04-ENDING_03,0))/:1 SALDO_04, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_05-ENDING_04,0))/:1 SALDO_05, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_06-ENDING_05,0))/:1 SALDO_06, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_07-ENDING_06,0))/:1 SALDO_07, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0))/:1 SALDO_08, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0))/:1 SALDO_09, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0))/:1 SALDO_10, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0))/:1 SALDO_11, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0))/:1 SALDO_12, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0))/:1 SALDO_13 from GL_INCOMRGD R (nolock) join ( select distinct ACCOUNT_NO from GL_INCOMRGD R1 left join OACT A on R1.ACCOUNT_NO = A.AcctCode WHERE CO_ID=':2' AND REPORT_NO = :3 AND LINE_TYPE='D' AND A.Levels = 1 and (FatherNum is null or trim(FatherNum) = '') ) R1 ON R.ACCOUNT_NO = R1.ACCOUNT_NO left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:6 and FISCAL_YEAR=:4 and CURR_ID=':5' AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=R.ACCOUNT_NO left join OACT A on R.ACCOUNT_NO = A.AcctCode left join sys_gcm s on s.CONDITION = 'ACCTYPE' and s.GCM_ID = a.AcctStrLe WHERE R.CO_ID=':2' AND REPORT_NO = :3 AND LINE_TYPE='D' AND A.Levels = 1 and (A.FatherNum is null or trim(A.FatherNum) = '') group by S.GCM_NOTE1
union all
select R.AcctName as TypeName, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0))/:1 SALDO_01, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0))/:1 SALDO_02, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_03-ENDING_02,0))/:1 SALDO_03, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_04-ENDING_03,0))/:1 SALDO_04, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_05-ENDING_04,0))/:1 SALDO_05, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_06-ENDING_05,0))/:1 SALDO_06, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_07-ENDING_06,0))/:1 SALDO_07, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0))/:1 SALDO_08, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0))/:1 SALDO_09, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0))/:1 SALDO_10, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0))/:1 SALDO_11, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0))/:1 SALDO_12, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0))/:1 SALDO_13 from oact R (nolock) join ( select top 1 ACC_IS from GL_SETUP (nolock) where CO_ID = ':2' ) G on R.AcctCode = G.ACC_IS left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=':2' and B.BR_ID=:6 and B.FISCAL_YEAR=:4 and B.CURR_ID=':5' AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=R.AcctCode group by R.AcctName

select LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0))/:6 SALDO_01, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0))/:6 SALDO_02, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_03-ENDING_02,0))/:6 SALDO_03, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_04-ENDING_03,0))/:6 SALDO_04, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_05-ENDING_04,0))/:6 SALDO_05, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_06-ENDING_05,0))/:6 SALDO_06, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_07-ENDING_06,0))/:6 SALDO_07, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0))/:6 SALDO_08, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0))/:6 SALDO_09, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0))/:6 SALDO_10, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0))/:6 SALDO_11, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0))/:6 SALDO_12, SUM(ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0))/:6 SALDO_13, COST_CENTER AS COST_CENTER from ( select LINE_NO,R.ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, BEGINNING_AMT,ENDING_01, ENDING_02, ENDING_03, ENDING_04, ENDING_05, ENDING_06, ENDING_07, ENDING_08, ENDING_09, ENDING_10, ENDING_11, ENDING_12, ENDING_13, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGD R (nolock) left join GL_BALANCE B (nolock) on B.CO_ID=R.CO_ID and B.BR_ID=:1 and FISCAL_YEAR=:2 and CURR_ID=':3' AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=R.ACCOUNT_NO :7 WHERE R.CO_ID=':4' AND REPORT_NO=:5 AND LINE_TYPE<>'P' ) T1 group by LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER union all select LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, sum(ENDING_01),sum(ENDING_02),sum(ENDING_03),sum(ENDING_04),sum(ENDING_05),sum(ENDING_06),sum(ENDING_07),sum(ENDING_08), sum(ENDING_09),sum(ENDING_10),sum(ENDING_11),sum(ENDING_12),sum(ENDING_13), COST_CENTER AS COST_CENTER FROM ( SELECT LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER AS COST_CENTER, ISNULL(ENDING_01-BEGINNING_AMT,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_01, ISNULL(ENDING_02-ENDING_01,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_02, ISNULL(ENDING_03-ENDING_02,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_03, ISNULL(ENDING_04-ENDING_03,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_04, ISNULL(ENDING_05-ENDING_04,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_05, ISNULL(ENDING_06-ENDING_05,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_06, ISNULL(ENDING_07-ENDING_06,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_07, ISNULL(ENDING_08-ENDING_07,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_08, ISNULL(ENDING_09-ENDING_08,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_09, ISNULL(ENDING_10-ENDING_09,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_10, ISNULL(ENDING_11-ENDING_10,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_11, ISNULL(ENDING_12-ENDING_11,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_12, ISNULL(ENDING_13-ENDING_12,0)*IIF(OPERATION='+',1,-1)/:6 ENDING_13 FROM ( select P.LINE_NO,X.ACCOUNT_NO,X.[DESCRIPTION],X.COLUMN_NO,X.FONT_STYLE,X.NOTES, BEGINNING_AMT,ENDING_01, ENDING_02, ENDING_03, ENDING_04, ENDING_05, ENDING_06, ENDING_07, ENDING_08, ENDING_09, ENDING_10, ENDING_11, ENDING_12, ENDING_13, OPERATION, IIF(':8' = 'C', '', B.COST_CENTER) AS COST_CENTER from GL_INCOMRGP P (nolock) LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD D (nolock) ON D.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND D.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND D.LINE_NO=P.FROM_LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_INCOMRGD X (nolock) ON X.CO_ID=P.CO_ID AND X.REPORT_NO=P.REPORT_NO AND X.LINE_NO=P.LINE_NO LEFT JOIN GL_BALANCE B (nolock) ON B.CO_ID=D.CO_ID AND B.BR_ID=:1 AND FISCAL_YEAR=:2 AND B.ACCOUNT_NO=D.ACCOUNT_NO AND CURR_ID=':3' :7 WHERE P.CO_ID=':4' AND P.REPORT_NO=:5 ) T2 ) Y group by LINE_NO,ACCOUNT_NO,[DESCRIPTION],COLUMN_NO,FONT_STYLE,NOTES, COST_CENTER ORDER BY LINE_NO
